Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你遭遇嚴寒侵襲時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When the cold comes for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血液會停止流向四肢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the blood stops running to your limbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它會流向軀干 保持臟器溫暖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It pools up inside to keep your organs warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的初戀情人告訴我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My first love told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個海上勞工 高高瘦瘦 體格強健\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An offshore roughnecker he was. Tall and lean, and tough as whitleather.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會說：“魯絲 你的微笑讓我溫暖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'd say, "Ruthie, your smile keeps me warm."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以千萬要保持微笑 直到我回來”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"So be sure to wear it till I'm home."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好 我們走吧 -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let's go. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-走起來 -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Move it. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 那玩意兒很厲害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, yeah, that was some shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著 嚴寒就會侵襲你的思想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Next, the cold comes for your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是你的意志力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And after that, your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet still,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心依然在抗爭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the heart fights on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魯絲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說威爾福德正在車尾搞什么勾當\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She says Wilford's up to something in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.38,0:02:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她走之后就沒了陽光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ Ain't no sunshine when she's gone ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在時就沒了溫暖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ It's not warm when she's away ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她走之后就沒了陽光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ Ain't no sunshine When she's gone ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她總是離開得太久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ And she's always gone too long ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次她離開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}♪ Anytime she goes away ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友們 今天是大日子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Big day, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是大日子 先生 測試需要的一切都準備好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Big day, sir. - Everything's ready for the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的黑得伍德醫生 親愛的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dear, poor Dr. Headwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那可憐的丈夫 黑得伍德醫生去世后 你還好嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you doing without our dear, poor Dr. Headwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺他依然跟我們在一起 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel he's still with us, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接手他以前的工作 你有信心嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you confident here, in his shoes as it were?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對有 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hundred percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 您看這身衣服行嗎  很有“曼哈頓計劃”的風范\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, how is this for the occasion? It's very, um, Manhattan Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下棉絨刷 把毛巾遞給我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put down the lint brush and hand me my towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失陪了 我們有很多工作要做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pardon me. We do have much to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那位海上勞工戀人過早地離開了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He left me too soon, my roughneck love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他工作的鉆井平臺塌了 所有的人都沉入了海底\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His rig went down with every man aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道在他獨自漂浮時 我的微笑讓他感到溫暖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know my smile kept him warm as he floated, all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:04:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道 在威爾福德這列 1023節車廂組成的列車上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just as I know our hearts will be the last thing to go
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的心將會是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on Wilford's train.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后屈服的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}1,023 cars long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有脫水癥狀 營養不良 而且血壓很低\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's, um, dehydrated, malnourished, her blood pressure's low.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可能有輻射中毒 所以…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's probably got radiation poisoning, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 想不想談談 在外面發生的那件事 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. You wanna talk about what happened out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想 你們倆差點就沒命了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, when you two almost died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個 是我們接吻的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, when we kissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就要當爸爸了 而且我答應過扎拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got a baby on the way, and I made a promise to Zarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不需要談那件事 -好 我也不需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I don't need to talk about it. - No, me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本拿到數據了 要不要去看看 這番鬧騰是否值得 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ben's got the data. Shall we see if it's been worth it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是不明白 她怎么可能在外面生存八年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I still don't get how it's possible to survive eight years out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用冰把自己封在室內\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You freeze yourself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著反應堆冷卻 靠剩余的電力維持生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Live off the residual power as the reactor cools.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說 這辦法太有才了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's kind of genius if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當初出去 都不是為了找她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not even why you went out there in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（宜居區）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果出來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have our results.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我估計這表情 不光是因為你的肋骨疼吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guessing that grimace isn't just from the ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟之前的差不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More of the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分析顯示該區域正在變暖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Analysis shows location is warming,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但變化速度不夠快 暫時還不宜居住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but the trend isn't steep enough to be habitable yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要等多久呢 本 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long are we talking, Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一個世紀  -差不多吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- A century? - Give or take.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是第五個點了 還是不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's O-for-five on this milk run.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.03,0:05:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 那就只剩最后一個地點了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, that leaves one more location.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉伯的那個暖點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your Arabian warm spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 從我們迄今為止 采集到的所有數據來看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. From all the data we've collected so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個地方實際上很有希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it looks actually pretty promising.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它位于這里 非洲之角 阿拉伯半島以南\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Located here, Horn of Africa, southern Arabian Peninsula.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 我們的食物不夠了 撐不到那里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We haven't enough food to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-現在我們又多了一張嘴 -該去奪回我們的列車了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We've got another mouth to feed. - It's time to get our train back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們找到他們 重新連接列車 然后帶大家一起去新的暖點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We find them, reconnect to the train, we lead everybody to the new hot spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟奪回列車相比 我更擔心奪回后能否保住它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm far less concerned with taking her, than keeping her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說得沒錯 我們這可是空手而歸啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's right. We're going back empty-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有新伊甸園存在的證據\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No proof of New Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有梅蘭妮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是空手而歸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not empty-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠非如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Far from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒 嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 別 沒事的 我能行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. No, it's okay. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 別緊張 沒事的 一切都好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, no, you're all right. Hey, you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 在這里 不需要穿防護服 看到嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, you don't need the suit here. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫安德烈雷頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My name's Andre Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們算是見過面了 在核電站時我們打了一架\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We kind of met already, uh, fighting in the nuclear plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得嗎 對不起 你會說英語嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You remember that? I'm sorry, do you speak English?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好點了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-阿莎 -阿莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Asha. - Asha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 你在這里是安全的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry, you're safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人會傷害你 你在雪國列車上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one's gonna hurt you, you're on Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪國列車 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Snowpiercer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在做夢嗎 \N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Am I… Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非我們大家都在做夢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not unless we all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那列車幸存下來了  -我帶你去看看吧 你能走嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The train survived? - Let me show you. Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在上面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她是什么人  -你已經沒資格提問了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is that? You lost the privilege to ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得了 貝絲 他們之前是在外面嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, come on, Bess. Were they outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腦袋怎么樣 估計很疼吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's your head? Bet it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒你打斷我鼻梁骨時那么疼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not as bad as when you broke my nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個偉大的工程師威爾福德先生呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where's Mr. Wilford, the Great Engineer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們其實不知道 現在有兩列列車了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, yeah, we don't know. There's two trains now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樓下有一個女人被關在一間牢房里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a woman in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這故事又長又復雜 你也有故事 我很想聽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a long, complicated story. You've got one too, and I wanna hear it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 目前最好是 一次消化一件事 相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it's better to take one thing at a time right now, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我憑什么要相信這些 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why should I trust any of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎登車 阿莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome aboard, Asha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放10%應該就能引起震撼 卻不會致命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ten percent should give us a nice jolt. Nothing too lethal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個水平很適合測試 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An appropriate test level, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤空的頭等車廂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the decommissioned First Class cars
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該能為電磁脈沖的沖擊 提供必要的緩沖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}should provide the necessary buffer from the EMP pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 凱文 我們來聽它“一展歌喉”吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, let's hear her sing, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始測試 釋放10%\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commence trial. Ten percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認 釋放10%\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Confirmed, ten percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始倒計時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Initiate countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始倒計時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Initiate countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都準備好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're all clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒計時開始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Initiating countdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩分鐘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你的小朋友帶回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brought your little friend back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是該離開這里嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shouldn't we get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我敢打賭那是某種武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd wager that it's a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.65,0:10:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它設在最后一節車廂里 那是列車重新連接的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's set in the very last car, right where the trains need to reconnect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定不會只是一個加熱器嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you sure it's not just a heater?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你沒事吧  -沒事 謝謝關心 我只是冷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You all right? - Yes, thanks. I'm just cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不該在外面跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's why you can't be running around out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能失去你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't afford to lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是整天躲在洞里 我還有什么用 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm no use to anyone hiding in a hole, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒數五、四\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in five, four,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三、二…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}three, two…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像某種電波從我體內穿過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Felt like some electrical wave went through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這就是那個武器了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think that was the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮 凱文 大家干得都漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well done, Kevin. Well done, crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-奧斯 這是怎么回事  -就…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Oz, what's going on? - Just…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我一點時間 我想…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just give me a second. I wanna…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想記住這一刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanna remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LJ…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}LJ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界很無情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's a mean old world,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but with you in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它終于有了意義\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it finally makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萊拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lilah Junior,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意嫁給我嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天啊 這顆鉆石真大 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Holy shit, that rock is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是 說來你可能不信 這可能是世上現存的最大的鉆石了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. It's actually crazy. It's probably the biggest diamond left in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-只用一雙厚襪子就換來了 -快給我戴上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- All it cost was a pair of heavy socks. - Put it on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得先說“我愿意”才行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gotta say yes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母去世后 我以為不會再有人愛我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't think anyone would love me after my parents died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 寶貝 我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know, baby. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得告訴威爾福德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to tell Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 出于尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. Out of respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就像我的家人一樣 我的意思是…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's the closest thing I have to family. I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你以外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萊拉和奧斯威勒先生來了 他們想見你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lilah Junior and Mr. Osweiller are here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶他們進來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, bring them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他戴著領帶呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He's wearing a tie. - Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我年輕的夜車居民們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My young denizens of the Nightcar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們能私下談談… -我們要結婚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Could we have a word in private-- - We're getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -我們想第一個告訴您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? - We wanted you to be the first to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LJ 親愛的 這真是驚喜啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}LJ, my dear, what a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給她戴上這么漂亮的戒指 是一項明智之舉 奧斯威勒先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Very wise to put such a nice ring on her finger, Mr. Osweiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.30,0:13:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有多久沒舉辦過婚禮了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When was the last time we had a wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是大事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is quite the occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許正是列車此刻所需要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps just the occasion the train needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們沒想大肆操辦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, we're not expecting anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們甚至都不… -我想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We don't even-- - I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該辦一場大婚禮 親愛的 人生的這一程太艱苦了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you should, my dear. Life's been so bloody dreary this leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會允許所有人都歇一個班次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll give everyone a shift off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提醒一下那些抱怨的人 團結是什么樣子的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's remind all the grumblers what unity looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提醒他們我們是同一列列車上的 忠誠會得到回報\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That we're all in this together, and loyalty is rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎么樣 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微歇口氣對大家有好處\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We could all use a little respite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-或許可以多分一兩份口糧… -太好了 那就定在明天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Maybe an extra ration or-- - Wonderful. Tomorrow then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 有何不可 沒時間臨陣退縮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Why not? No time for cold feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LJ 我們要讓夜車煥然一新\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll transform the Nightcar, LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者我該稱呼你為 “奧斯威勒太太” \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or should I say, Mrs. Osweiller?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗爾杰-奧斯威勒 \N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Oh… Folger-Osweiller? - Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常順口 我要用層層的紅色天鵝絨來布置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rolls off the tongue. I'm seeing red velvet, layers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎拉 去找糕點師\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ah… Zarah, go see the Cakemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你把糕點師貶入堆肥區了 -那就把他弄出來 我們要舉辦婚禮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You put the Cakemaker in Compost. - Then get him out. We're getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.98,0:14:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（忠臣大婚 ）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給他沖個澡 他做糕點需要什么 就去面包房拿 明白嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get him a shower and anything he needs from the bakery, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（全列車公假）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這里干什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the hell are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德在造武器 你知道這事嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilford's building a weapon. You know anything about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他在策劃什么 但不知道武器的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know he's up to something, but no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.17,0:15:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯絲看到哈維在制造那個武器 所以她想跟他取得聯系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, Ruth saw Javi working on it, so she wants to make contact with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴過你們了 哈維不愿跟我說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you guys, Javi won't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從被那只狗咬過之后 他整個人就變了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He hasn't been the same since that dog attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰沒個傷疤呢  這是魯絲的決定 她想見他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we all got scars. It's Ruth's call. She wants to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砸顯示器也不會讓衛星與地球同步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hitting the monitor does not tend to affect the satellite's geosync.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能讓我感覺好受些 不過我們大家都不在狀態\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What it does do is make me feel better, but we're all falling out of orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本 我們要怎么在大海里撈到針呢 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you find a needle in a haystack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝天謝地 只是一片大海而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank God, it's only a haystack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你有什么見解嗎  -只有一個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You have any theories? - I have one theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在跟蹤我們 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That he is following us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一心理假設真不錯啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a pretty good psychological assumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將在一天左右回到主軌道 經過這里時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he is following us, we're back on the main line in a day or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的衛星覆蓋范圍會有所改善 如果他在跟蹤我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As we came through here, our satellite coverage improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許我們就能探測到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we see him then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也能探測到我們 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he sees us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽要是看到你昨天 駕馭列車時的表現 會很驕傲的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your mum would be proud of how you handled the train yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不這么認為 本 不過謝謝你這么說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't really think so, Ben, but thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉 我們找到了一個幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alex, we found a survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許希望出現奇跡并無不可\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we can hope for a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經死了 本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's gone, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說說她是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me who she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少告訴我你在找什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At least tell me what you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（沙特阿拉伯 蘇丹）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到了什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（又做了一個夢）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just, uh, in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（乘務員）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為你布置了一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've made it up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真暖和啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's, uh… It's so warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-謝謝你… -我叫喬西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Thank you, uh… - Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Josie. Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我已經很久沒說話了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sorry, it's, uh… It's been a long time since I spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 會慢慢熟練起來的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's all right. It'll all come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你活下來了 我的意思是…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You made it. I mean… Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你離被凍死最近的一次有多近 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How close you ever come to freezing to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟多數人差不多吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess no less than most of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那經歷跟大家說的一樣嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it like they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你開始放松 開始覺得暖和\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You start to relax. It goes warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會看到一些東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說樹 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like, uh, trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍血樹 青草\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dragon's blood tree. Grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感覺到陽光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I could feel the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我們在找的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was the place we're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興你活過來了 因為那不是我們在找的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm glad you came back 'cause it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 聽著 這種樹只在亞丁灣生長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, look, these trees only grow in the Gulf of Aden,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞丁灣就在阿拉伯暖點的中間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}right here in the middle of our Arabian warm spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前從沒聽說過龍血樹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd never even heard of a dragon's blood tree before,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我卻看到了它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說你看到了未來 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you saying you had a vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我只是在告訴你當時發生的事 -你告訴過別人嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'm just telling you what happened. - You tell anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒有 -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持正常狀態\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep it on the rails.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當時差點沒命了 所以記憶中的某些東西閃現了出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You had a close call, something popped out of your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中時學過的某種樹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some tree you learned about in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 你或許是對的 謝謝提點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Yeah, you're probably right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一樣 又經歷一次瀕死體驗 對嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Another day, another near-death experience, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我愛你 哥們 -嗯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Love you, buddy. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱文 今天我們的攻勢與往日不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're on a different tack today, Kevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要發起魅力攻勢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A charm offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎么樣 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太紅了嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Too much red?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色永不嫌夠 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never enough red, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你為什么要那么說  -說什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Why'd you say that? - Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說什么了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“弗爾杰-奧斯威勒”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Folger-Osweiller."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是那么一說而已 沒想到他會記到登記簿上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just said it. I didn't know he'd put it on the register.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 這下他成了婚禮的主角\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, it's his wedding now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我就知道他會這么做 -那又怎樣 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I knew he'd do this. - So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一天 我們將會享受 國王和王后的待遇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We get to be king and queen of everything for a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在利用我們 LJ\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's using us, LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在我們身上作投資\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's investing in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦一場小小的儀式 我就很開心了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would've been very happy with something small.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你唱首歌 就幾個朋友在場 但這是不可能的 對嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sing you a song, a few of us. That wasn't on the table, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 因為我們沒有朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, because we don't have any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望我們成為大腕夫婦 有一天我們可能會管理這列列車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanna be in a power couple. We could run this train one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-天啊 LJ  -怎么了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- LJ, Jesus! - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年邁的人不斷死去 都快沒有年輕人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Old people keep dying off, there's barely any young people left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快 就得由我們來統領他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And soon, we'll have to rule them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我們的婚禮啊 你就從不停止算計嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's our wedding day. Do you ever stop conniving?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-算計是好事 -好吧 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Conniving is good. - Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.37,0:22:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去算計吧 現在想取消已經太遲了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Connive away! It's too late to call it off now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為提出取消 威爾福德就會 把我的腦袋凍掉 對嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'cause Wilford would have my head out a port, wouldn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣甩手走開 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't walk away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧斯 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oz?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈維 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Javi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.08,0:22:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈維 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Javi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以跟我說話的 這里沒有別人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can talk to me. No one is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工程師 威爾福德要你去頭等車廂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Engineer, Wilford wants you down in First.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我在上班呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'm on shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 他要你去的 所以設成自動駕駛 快去就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. That's what he wants, so put it on autopilot and off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.33,0:23:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看上去很漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You look beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是你的大日子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's your big day. - Would you leave it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能別去管它了嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care if it looks like shit. Just leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎它是否亂糟糟的 別去管它就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, dear. I heard the bride might be blue, but blue in the face?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.54,0:23:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 我聽說過新娘子會有婚前憂郁 不知道還會大發脾氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我先出去了 -好 那樣最好 謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, that will be best, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.80,0:23:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 來 告訴我你在為什么生氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, now, here. Now, tell me what you fought about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:23:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“你總是在算計” 他覺得我又自私又冷酷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"You're always conniving." He thinks I'm selfish and I'm cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.06,0:23:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候我不得不那樣 不是嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to be sometimes, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想讓你待在夜車上 LJ\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's why I wanted you in the Nightcar, LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.32,0:23:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個現實主義者 你知道有人受傷是難免的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a realist. You understand someone always gets hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.70,0:24:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 我雖然不會大聲說出來 但“這就是生活”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, it's like, I don't say it out loud, but c'est la vie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.16,0:24:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他或許還覺得 整場婚禮都被我接管了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He also probably thinks I'm taking over the whole ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.46,0:24:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白為什么 你們的婚禮對我很重要嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you understand why your wedding is important to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.09,0:24:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫你管束大家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Helps keep everyone in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.34,0:24:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 他們會看到 只有一種辦事方法 就是我的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. They see there's only one way, the way I do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.01,0:24:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 在這列列車上 有一樣東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see, on the train, the old laws and morality,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.51,0:24:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比舊法和道德更重要 它是什么 \N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}they don't matter as much as… what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.98,0:24:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-忠誠 -沒錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Loyalty. - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.65,0:24:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對列車的忠誠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Loyalty to the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.11,0:24:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你這假惺惺的眼淚 留著到婚禮上流吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, save the crocodile tears for the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.11,0:24:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我 好好表演一番\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make a show of it, for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.16,0:24:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.28,0:24:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.96,0:24:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚床放在這里很不錯呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lovely spot for your wedding bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.88,0:25:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝夸獎 是我們自己布置的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you. We, uh, did it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.18,0:25:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.43,0:25:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐 來啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sit down. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.56,0:25:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕激昂的愛情 我很熟悉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Young, tumultuous love, I know it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.19,0:25:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我指的是激昂的部分 我已經不再年輕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the tumultuous part, not the young bit anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.99,0:25:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 LJ不開心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But LJ's upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.03,0:25:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 這個嘛…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, it's, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.04,0:25:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是婚前緊張\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pre-wedding jitters.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.87,0:25:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會沒事的 是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll be fine. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.04,0:25:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對她有很強的保護意識\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I am rather protective of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.09,0:25:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我好好查閱了一下 羅齊先生的人事記錄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I had a long look at Mr. Roche's personnel records,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.88,0:25:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當制動員的時候 很會把握各種機會嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you were an opportunistic boy in blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.39,0:25:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我經營過幾份副業 是的 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, ran a few side hustles. Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.35,0:25:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個劣跡斑斑的企業家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, an entrepreneur with a vicious streak.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.73,0:25:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當夜車經理的優良品質\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good qualities in a Nightcar manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.11,0:25:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.19,0:25:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙手…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}these hands…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.65,0:26:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻能彈奏如此動聽的鋼琴曲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}play piano so beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.70,0:26:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心里有點渴望成為一名藝術家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Part of you just yearns to be an artiste,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.54,0:26:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顫聲吟唱最悲傷的歌曲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}warbling the saddest of songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.25,0:26:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在所謂的 富有創造性的環境中長大的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I didn't grow up in what you'd call a creative environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.55,0:26:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你表達了自己的心聲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You found your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.42,0:26:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴師 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Piano man, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.30,0:26:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那紅發妻子則負責吧臺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And his ginger wife behind the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.76,0:26:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是我的團隊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're my team here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.39,0:26:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點我們明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.94,0:26:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We do.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.32,0:26:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們制動員搜身的手法 還記得嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your Brakeman shakedown move, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.86,0:26:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也抓我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Squeeze mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.86,0:26:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 抓吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on. Squeeze them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.53,0:26:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.58,0:26:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再用力點 用上所有的勁道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harder. Give them some basso profundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.83,0:26:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你的雙手是用來干什么的 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, what are your hands for, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.05,0:26:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捏碎別人的蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Crushing balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.55,0:27:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要用來愛撫你的妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And caressing your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.56,0:27:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后 你想怎么彈琴都行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When that's done, by all means, tickle the ivories.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.95,0:27:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你非常有才華\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because you're very talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.83,0:27:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真心話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.84,0:27:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.10,0:27:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.13,0:28:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德拉托爾先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. De la Torre.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.93,0:28:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.68,0:28:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.35,0:28:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯絲 可你…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ruth? But you…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.85,0:28:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該在另一列列車上呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're on the other train.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.27,0:28:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我一直都在這里 幫助乘客們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I've been here the whole time. I've been helping the passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.40,0:28:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為我們在外面的朋友盡己所能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Doing my bit for our friends out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.69,0:28:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不該在這里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.32,0:28:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈維\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Javi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.20,0:28:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我很抱歉… -不…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Oh, I'm sorry-- - No, no, no…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.66,0:28:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工程師 我只是要你幫忙 拜托了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Engineer, I just… I just need your help, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.58,0:28:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在列車后部做的那個東西 它是什么 它能做什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The thing that you're working on back there, what is it? What does it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.75,0:29:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能徹底阻止雷頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's gonna stop Layton dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.84,0:29:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我得回狗那里去了 抱歉 -不 先別走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I need to go back to the dog, I'm sorry. - No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.26,0:29:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得告訴我它是怎么運作的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.55,0:29:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不  -哈維 哈維 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. No! No! - Javi? Javi!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.70,0:29:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美極了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.59,0:29:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎 勇敢的乘客們 工人們 及其他所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome, brave passengers, workers, all now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.84,0:29:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興大家能暫停手頭的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's my great pleasure to pause our labors,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.84,0:29:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花點時間團聚在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and spend time in union.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.14,0:29:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們匯聚一堂 是為了慶祝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The union today by marriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.64,0:30:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小萊拉弗爾杰 和約翰克里斯多夫奧斯威勒喜結良緣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of Lilah Folger Junior and John Christopher Osweiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.36,0:30:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 最近這段行程 非常寒冷 供給不足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know these have been cold miles of deprivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.45,0:30:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀律嚴酷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And discipline is harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.24,0:30:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都得了凍瘡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've paid in frostbite,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.83,0:30:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所愛的人因流感而喪生 愿他們安息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and loved ones lost to influenza. May they rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.08,0:30:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 該是慶祝勝利的時候了 不是嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So it's time we celebrate a win, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.76,0:30:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳統的婚姻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Old World matrimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.80,0:30:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 把酒杯倒滿 我們有足夠的酒 大家都有份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone, fill a glass. There's enough for every soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.56,0:30:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有額外的熱餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Extra hot food too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.77,0:30:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我去去就回 -好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I'll be back. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.35,0:30:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓全車上下 都為萊拉和約翰舉起酒杯吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raise a glass up and down our train for Lilah and John.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.73,0:30:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 干杯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.57,0:30:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 各位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.07,0:30:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再敬我們與列車牢不可破的協議\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To our unbreakable pact with the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.99,0:30:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬忠誠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To loyalty
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.45,0:31:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及你們與我的約定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and your contract with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.92,0:31:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.38,0:31:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威爾福德 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wilford! Wilford!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.98,0:31:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽上去像是一種電磁脈沖武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sounds like an electromagnetic pulse weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.40,0:31:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒有真正見過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never actually seen one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.02,0:31:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-但你知道它的運作原理吧  -知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- But you do know how it works? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.44,0:31:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能發出電磁脈沖 破壞雪國列車上的所有電子設備\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It sends out an electromagnetic pulse killing the electronics on Snowpiercer,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.87,0:31:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓雷頓的列車無法前進\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}leaving Layton dead in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.33,0:31:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那趁著這場婚禮 我們來設法阻止那種情況發生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So while this wedding is happening, let's try and make it not do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.54,0:31:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有操作手冊嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You got a manual?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.46,0:31:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 光明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on, Lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.83,0:31:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟魯絲說你很擅長這類活兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told the lady you're good at this kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.00,0:31:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除電磁脈沖武器 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Disarming EMPs?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.92,0:31:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.35,0:32:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.36,0:32:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈維 你要去哪兒 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where you going, Javi?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.57,0:32:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回狗那里去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Back to the dog. - Ah-ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.40,0:32:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才去哪兒了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.11,0:32:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集最后一套數據\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Final data collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.37,0:32:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能走了嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.59,0:32:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.55,0:32:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.35,0:32:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.89,0:32:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 我要你們完成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, I ask you to take the sacred steps
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.35,0:32:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與永恒機車相結合的神圣儀式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in union with the Eternal Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.94,0:32:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這四步代表了人類所經歷的歷程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These four steps represent the path humanity has taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.03,0:33:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從青草\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From grass
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.83,0:33:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到寒冰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.37,0:33:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-從寒冰到鋼鐵 -從寒冰到鋼鐵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- From ice to steel. - From ice to steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.67,0:33:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從鋼鐵到…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And from steel to the lights…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.96,0:33:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒機車的燈光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the Eternal Engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.39,0:33:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人來過這里嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyone come through here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.22,0:33:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個被狗咬了臉的工程師常來這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That dog-faced engineer's here all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.31,0:33:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他很快就會出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he's in and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.85,0:33:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是要進去看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we'll check it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.19,0:33:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人會覺得這場婚禮 是他們行動的好時機 不是嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wouldn't this wedding be a great distraction for the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.32,0:33:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不知道要怎么解除這玩意兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have no idea how to disarm this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.78,0:33:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就各處擺弄一下唄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just start messing with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.24,0:33:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這就是你的計劃  -你才是我的計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's your plan? - You're my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.79,0:33:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍靴和待客部的人來了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jackboots and teal coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.29,0:33:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -我們會被困在這里的 快離開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? - They'll pin us back here. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.21,0:33:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得走了 快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We gotta go. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.13,0:33:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-來呀 -不行 你們得繼續解除武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Come on. - No. You need to keep working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.17,0:33:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算干什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.42,0:34:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去干擾他們 否則大家都會被困在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll need to run interference or we're all stuck back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.60,0:34:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們看到了我 就不會進到這里來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They won't keep coming if they see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.39,0:34:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只管解除這武器 給雷頓一個戰斗機會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just disable it, and give Layton a fighting chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.56,0:34:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-魯絲… -派克先生 這是命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ruth-- - That is an order, Mr. Pike.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.27,0:34:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在由你來負責了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're in charge now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.65,0:34:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我信任你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.32,0:34:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.46,0:34:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.10,0:34:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.68,0:34:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 凱文 是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, Kevin. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.48,0:34:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直以來都在找的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The one you've been looking for all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.31,0:34:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你像只沒頭蒼蠅一樣到處瞎找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Running around like a chicken with your head cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.69,0:34:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我來投降了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.78,0:35:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又冷又餓 所以 動手吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm cold and I'm starving. So, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.78,0:35:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不費吹灰之力 你就能當上英雄了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You get to be the hero without ever lifting a finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.12,0:35:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她帶走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.14,0:35:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初我們有34個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There were 34 of us to start,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.90,0:35:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依靠核電站的剩余電力竭力維持\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}eking it out on the plant's residual power.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.65,0:35:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是韓國科學家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Korean scientists,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.69,0:35:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及像我這樣的外國核技術人員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}foreign nuclear technicians like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.70,0:35:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我們的一些家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some of our families too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.91,0:35:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掠奪者死光之前 殺死了我們大約一半的人 然后…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marauders killed about half of us before they died out. And then--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.96,0:35:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掠奪者 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marauders?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.92,0:36:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后嚴寒或輻射中毒 奪走了其余人的性命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then the cold or radiation poisoning took the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.88,0:36:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我侄子當時是15歲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My nephew, he was 15 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.09,0:36:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是最后一個死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was the last to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.39,0:36:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他得了甲狀腺癌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He had thyroid cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.77,0:36:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后 他在求我把他殺了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By the end, he was begging me to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.77,0:36:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是大約四年前的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was about four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.86,0:36:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}After that…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.61,0:36:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.24,0:36:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就沒有了時間的概念\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I lost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.07,0:36:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再抱有希望 不再去想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I stopped hoping, stopped thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.82,0:36:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我之外還有其他人住在那下面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's like someone other than me lived down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.12,0:36:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我看見了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then I turned my eyes on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.79,0:36:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉地告訴你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hate to tell you this,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.50,0:36:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你與世隔絕期間 人類并沒怎么進化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but humankind hasn't exactly evolved in your absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.76,0:36:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甘冒生命危險 甚至不顧理智 就為了救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You pushed past what was safe, even sane, to rescue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.01,0:36:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.85,0:36:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興自己那么做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just glad I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.28,0:37:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是基本沒有信號\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're still basically blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.11,0:37:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上次到這里時還有衛星圖像的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We had picture last time we came out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.03,0:37:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-衛星信號在持續減弱 -說說其他選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The satellites continue to degrade. - Options?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.87,0:37:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我們有其他選擇 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wait, there's options?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.37,0:37:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們直接回到主軌道上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We go back directly to the main line,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.71,0:37:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候 如果他們在我們前面 我們就會看到跡象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where we either see physical signs they're in front of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.29,0:37:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然 我們就知道他們在后面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or we know they're behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.17,0:37:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者我們可以與主軌道平行前進\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or we parallel the main line,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.25,0:37:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望信號會變好 能讓我們在衛星圖像上探測到他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}hoping the signal improves enough so we can glimpse them on the sat.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.93,0:37:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-選第二個方法 -遵命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Second route. - Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.52,0:37:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才那樣決定的依據是什么 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, um, you picked that based on what?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.61,0:37:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又看到了未來 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Another vision?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.57,0:37:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不上主軌道 我們會有更多選擇的余地 對嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I mean, there's gotta be more options off the main line, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.49,0:37:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.05,0:38:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她為我們犧牲了自己 所以現在我們得解除這玩意兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She sacrificed for us. So now, we gotta kill this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.76,0:39:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好嗎  -這是筆記本電腦的連接口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Okay? - The laptop patch is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.23,0:39:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒法黑入它的軟件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we can't hack the software.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.90,0:39:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們可以中斷電源 擾亂它的供電\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we can disrupt the power supply, mess with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.61,0:39:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這好像是裝載程序面板\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks like an arming sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.71,0:39:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-它被激活了 -糟糕 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's live. - Oh, shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.42,0:39:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我覺得它處于全脈沖狀態 -是 我看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I think it's at full pulse. - I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.71,0:39:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒法把它關了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't turn it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.09,0:39:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停不下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.80,0:39:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧…\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.39,0:39:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早知道會是一個 對鐵路后勤具有敏銳洞察力的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew it had to be someone with acumen for rail logistics.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.52,0:39:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但老實說 更令我欽佩的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But to be honest, I'm more impressed with how low you went
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.15,0:39:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然會如此屈尊 跟末等人混在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to grovel it out in the bowels.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.49,0:39:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在盡量不辜負期望 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I do try not to disappoint, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.16,0:40:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能保持忠誠該多好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you'd only stayed loyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.33,0:40:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是忠誠的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am loyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.29,0:40:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的忠誠給了比你更重要的東西 威爾福德先生 你全搞錯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To something bigger than you. You've got it all wrong, Mr. Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.63,0:40:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話我一直聽到 但我還是贏了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hear that all the time, and then I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.59,0:40:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏和領導是兩回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Winning isn't leading.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.01,0:40:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光有忠誠還不夠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Loyalty isn't enough on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.72,0:40:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還需要有愛 不是你享受的那種敬畏之愛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It has to come with love. And not the kind that you feed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.97,0:40:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是無條件的愛 愿為每一個乘客犧牲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unconditional love. Sacrifice, for each and every passenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.68,0:40:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-老天  -你不能忽視愛的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, God! - You can't ignore love.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.90,0:40:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也無法預測它的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't predict it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.15,0:40:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我們得把這玩意兒 送出那扇門去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We gotta get this thing out that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.28,0:40:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-沒有開門的密碼 也沒防護服 -我在想辦法呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- We don't have door codes or breach suits. - Uh, thinking. Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.49,0:40:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二年那場叛亂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Year two rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.45,0:40:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們封了通勤車的門不讓我們上 但我們弄壞了鉸鏈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They sealed the subtrain doors on us, but we compromised the hinges.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.29,0:40:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.37,0:40:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.71,0:40:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強壯男孩 準備好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Strong Boy, get it ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.43,0:40:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 解除了 來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Clear. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.55,0:41:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動手吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.27,0:41:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.39,0:41:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們此刻正在為你準備門洞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're preparing the port for you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.56,0:41:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會確保他們把臂銬放高夾緊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll make sure they mount the cuff nice and high
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.61,0:41:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你將來沒法裝假肢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where prosthetics are impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.45,0:41:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也不會戴假肢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wouldn't wear one anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.54,0:41:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 你好了嗎 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on. You got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.16,0:41:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 快跑 姐妹 快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, run. Run, sister, run.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.51,0:41:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.36,0:41:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諷刺的是 我當初建門洞 只是一種虛聲恫嚇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The irony is, I built the ports in as an idle threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.49,0:42:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒想過要使用它們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never expected to use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.53,0:42:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你卻用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You did.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.78,0:42:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thirteen times.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.33,0:42:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意贖罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll pay my penance.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.84,0:42:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的手臂凍掉吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can have my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.54,0:42:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很好奇那會是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Whoa. - Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.00,0:42:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是電磁波 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wonder, what on earth could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.71,0:43:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在三角定位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Electromagnetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.13,0:43:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是特征痕跡 一定是他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Triangulating.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.47,0:43:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that's the signature. It's gotta be them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.39,0:43:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們西側520公里處\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, it is. Five hundred and twenty kilometers west.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.68,0:43:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在主軌道上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're on the main line.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.31,0:43:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這比在衛星圖像上找到他們強多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a lot better than seeing them on sat.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.31,0:43:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 也就是說威爾福德看不到我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah? So it means Wilford can't see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.15,0:43:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們比他有優勢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got the drop on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.73,0:43:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-威爾福德討厭意外之事 -很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Well, Wilford hates surprises. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.53,0:43:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去給他一個“驚喜”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go give him one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.30,0:43:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為你們做了一樣東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I built something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.02,0:43:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣本可以挽救無數性命的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something that would have saved countless lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.02,0:43:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們本可以不費一顆彈藥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We could have snuffed out Layton's pirate train
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.90,0:44:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就毀掉雷頓的強盜列車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without firing a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.07,0:44:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今 就因為一個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, thanks to a rat
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.95,0:44:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在管道中的叛徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}found hiding in the pipes,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.99,0:44:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭爆發時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when this war comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.25,0:44:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們將會有傷亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're all going to bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.00,0:44:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因為你 這場戰爭 又將回到原始的打斗方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's back to broadswords and shields because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.22,0:44:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生 好了 隨時可以行刑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ready when you are, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.06,0:44:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就凍斷它吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's get it bloody off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.55,0:45:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're back. They're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.86,0:45:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-去戰斗崗位  -快走 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Battle stations! - Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.36,0:45:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去戰斗崗位 狗崽子們 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Battle stations, you dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.28,0:45:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
